name: The love of the moon and the sun
description:
Don't ask if I love you.
Don't ask if lve ever been interested in you.
Don't try to grab me by you side.
Don't cry because of me.
Stop love me moon.
Who say the sun is so great and majestic to it's so lonely.
Even though l love you with allmyheart but I can't let you my side pretend l don't  care not because I don't love you but I can't let you get burned by mine
